"""app.py — Exposure & Collateral Engine (SINGLE-FILE BUILD).

A complete, self-contained Streamlit app that reads two (or more) Excel
files, validates them, runs configurable business calculations, and shows a
formatted output table with copy / Excel / CSV export.

Everything lives in this one file, organised into clearly-marked sections so
it stays maintainable. In day-to-day use you only edit two of them:

    ┌─ SECTION 1  CONFIG ............ headers, sheet names, output layout,
    │                                 formatting, highlighting  ← EDIT HERE
    ├─ SECTION 2  UTILS ............. logging, timing, byte helpers
    ├─ SECTION 3  EXCEL READER ...... read workbooks / sheets
    ├─ SECTION 4  VALIDATION ........ config-driven, friendly errors
    ├─ SECTION 5  CALCULATIONS ...... business formulas only         ← EDIT HERE
    ├─ SECTION 6  OUTPUT FORMATTER .. build + format the output table
    ├─ SECTION 7  PROCESSING ........ workflow coordinator
    ├─ SECTION 8  SAMPLE DATA ....... generate dummy test workbooks
    └─ SECTION 9  STREAMLIT UI ...... widgets, buttons, display

Run with:
    pip install streamlit pandas numpy openpyxl
    streamlit run app.py
"""

